h the like button.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"steve_v","CreatedById":69272,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-08-16T08:04:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223434586\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221534392244\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022176173\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The_Cat_In_Space\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, The_Cat_In_Space said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you like and then unlike something, and then like it again, will the person who\u0027s content you\u0027re liking be receiving a notification every time you like their thing?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI wonder if there is a rate-limit on that... Tempting to script up a wee test. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-08-16T12:34:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust FYI, in extreme cases, people have been warned/banned for abusing forum \u0022features\u0022 like that. So probably not a good idea.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Minmus Derp","CreatedById":187595,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-08-16T12:36:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan there be a spaaaaaaaace background?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-08-16T13:33:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, to jump off of what \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshove